✨ Features

🔐 Authentication

- User Registration
- Secure Login System
- JWT Authentication
- Password Encryption using bcrypt
- Protected Routes

💬 Real-Time Messaging

- Instant Message Delivery
- Private One-to-One Chat
- Real-Time Typing Indicators
- Message Timestamp
- Online / Offline Status
- Read Receipts

👥 User Management

- Search Users
- User Profiles
- Contact List
- Recent Conversations

📁 Media Support

- Image Uploads
- File Sharing
- Profile Picture Upload
- Media Preview

🎨 Modern User Interface

- WhatsApp Inspired Design
- Responsive Layout
- Mobile Friendly
- Dark Mode Support
- Smooth Animations

⚡ Performance

- Real-Time Communication with Socket.io
- Optimized State Management
- Fast API Responses
- Lazy Loading Components

